name: Greek-style Quesadillas
description: A taste of Greece in a tortilla! Wonderful with prepared Dillicious Tzatziki for dipping.
preparation: Lay out tortillas on counter top.
Combined next 5 ingredients in small mixing bowl. Divide mixture on one half of each tortilla. Fold tortillas in half with firm pressure.
Lightly spray frying pan with olive oil. Cook quesadillas 4 minutes on each side. Cut each into 3 wedges and serve.
Quesadillas can also be baked on a Sheet Pan lined with a Sheet Pan Liner at 350° F (175° C), until tortillas are golden and cheese in melted.

products.name: Chicken Souvlaki Seasoning (Pkg of 3)
summary: A Greek-inspired meal, souvlaki is marinated meat grilled on a skewer, often served with warm pita bread and tzatziki. No grill? No problem. Skip the skewers and put your Sheet Pan to work to make equally tasty Chicken Souvlaki in 20 minutes in the oven.
